author: eTN Global Editor
title: Magnitude 7.3 earthquake rocks Vanuatu
text:
Magnitude 7.3 earthquake rocks Vanuatu 
Strong earthquake rocked Vanuatu today. 
Preliminary Earthquake Report 
Date-Time • 20 Oct 2015 21:52:02 UTC 
• 21 Oct 2015 08:52:02 near epicenter 
Location 14.861S 167.307E 
Distances • 34 km (21 mi) NE of Port-Olry, Vanuatu 
• 75 km (46 mi) NNE of Luganville, Vanuatu • 335 km (207 mi) NNW of Port-Vila, Vanuatu • 670 km (415 mi) N of We, New Caledonia • 810 km (502 mi) N of Paita, New Caledonia 
Location Uncertainty Horizontal: 7.6 km; Vertical 5.6 km Parameters Nph = 111; Dmin = 66.0 km; Rmss = 0.85 seconds; Gp = 32° Oct 20, 2015
